text: Jonathan Dubas (born 4 March 1991) is a Swiss professional basketball player.Jonathan Dubas joins Leuven Bears, COURT SIDE NEWSPAPER, 3 May 2013. Accessed 30 Aug 2016. He currently plays for the Norrköping Dolphins of the Basketligan in Sweden. Dubas re-signed with the team on 27 August 2018.
